# Changelog

## [0.1.4] - 2024-07-02

 - modified trainig loop of model to include test set. I also freeze more weights now
 - added a function to classify a new image and return category (needs to be added to the proper analysis function)

## [0.1.4] - 2024-06-25

### Added
- a training loop to train pytorch model to classify dog breeds. -> need to implement it to a function to classify new images
- saved model with weights, works quite well, but could be trained further.

## [0.1.3] - 2024-06-22

### Added

- Enabling of download as a package

### Improved

- GUI

### Fixed

- CLI (added --help and --version commands)

## [0.1.2] - 2024-06-11

### Added

- Containerization via Docker

## [0.1.1] - 2024-06-4

### Added

- First Graphical User Interface (very basic)

## [0.1.0] - 2024-05-11

### Added

- Commmand Line Interface (except --help and --version)

## [0.0.3] - 2024-05-11

### Added

- functions for analyzing: imageToNumpyArray, get_image_shape
- configuration file
- .gitignore file

### Removed

- ideas folder

## [0.0.2] - 2024-05-7

### Added

- tests for processing and analysis functions

## [0.0.1] - 2024-04-23

### Added

- requirements.txt
- functions for loading images: load_image_as_PILimage, load_image_as_numpy_array, load_image_as_PILimage_from_numpy_array, load_image_as_numpy_array_from_PILimage
- functions for saving images: saveImage, saveNumpyArrayAsImage
- functions for processing: rotate, mirror, blur, edge_enhance, find_edges, smooth
- ideas folder for brainstorming
